cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with object tracking in LIDAR point clouds using deep learning techniques. The paper focuses on using a 2D-3D Siamese network for efficient tracking proposals. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with robotics and autonomous vehicles, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper uses deep learning techniques, which is a subfield of machine learning, and hence cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also involves the use of regularization techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for text summarization, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
